>\n可以down定uber<br />\n仲可以call電單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd459d50fef7226423f76e5d994ca2c2ada3791b","tid":403714,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T18:22:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去sapa建議3日2夜 因為搭入去/出嚟都要好耐時間<br />\n圖片方面自己search <br />\n下龍灣果啲自己上agoda search Cruise 通常包食玩住交通</blockquote><br />\n下龍好ON9. 陸龍未去過.<br />\n首選SAPA.<br />\n去下龍記得去埋塗山叫雞.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a53c20ccd99a2f390c902959d4718d135a22d9fe","tid":403714,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T18:24:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲的士真係亂尻咁收錢<br />\n可以down定uber<br />\n仲可以call電單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我上次去, 未坐過的士. <br />\n全程都係行. 日日行十幾二十公里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65753c063b457e201c7d8b36835c23997cc8cb1d","tid":403714,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T18:26:18.000Z","msg":"去沙霸行山行啦 <br />\n下龍灣食海鮮都好撚貴"},{"pid":"f086db3f6f549e08727068b6f4a587627945a221","tid":403714,"uid":33843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T03:40:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去sapa建議3日2夜 因為搭入去/出嚟都要好耐時間<br />\n圖片方面自己search <br />\n下龍灣果啲自己上agoda search Cruise 通常包食玩住交通</blockquote><br />\n下龍好ON9. 陸龍未去過.<br />\n首選SAPA.<br />\n去下龍記得去埋塗山叫雞.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsapa <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f1d614675c2d99a343d4bca3c5534e44cc393b2","tid":403714,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T07:12:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去沙霸行山行啦 <br />\n下龍灣食海鮮都好撚貴</blockquote><br />\nSAPA而家有CABLE CAR上. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}